<item>
            <title>[HIVE-25275] OOM during query planning due to HiveJoinPushTransitivePredicatesRule matching infinitely</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-25275</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While running the following query OOM is raised during the planning phase&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt; (`value_date` &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt;) STORED &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; ORC;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; B (`business_date` &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt;) STORED &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; ORC;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;.VALUE_DATE
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;, B
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;.VALUE_DATE = BUSINESS_DATE
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;AND&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;.VALUE_DATE = TRUNC(BUSINESS_DATE, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
